:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"【建議】<br />\n推俾樓主<br />\n只要香港主要交通幹道用唔到，就會配合罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n1. 香城紅磡海底隧道<br />\n集合點1:理工大學門口<br />\n集合點2:維多利亞公園銅鑼灣入口噴水池<br />\n<br />\n2. 香城東區海底隧道/東區走廊<br />\n集合點：鰂魚涌公園<br />\n<br />\n3. 香城獅子山隧道<br />\n集合點：浸會大學善衡校園<br />\n<br />\n4. 香城大老山隧道<br />\n集合點：牛池灣公園<br />\n<br />\n預計凌晨開始集合，清晨六點開始行動"},{"pid":"bda44e2b749a85546a0f2a2a2d41bc6c49766f24","tid":1377600,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:00:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff09696aa2664e2c42a9ae335b2c048b96ca5aba","tid":1377600,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a64bcdd6a3dd03ebbee900bc80b50b80753fee","tid":1377600,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"805好啲，易宣傳同造勢"},{"pid":"3ccc75e4a47ccdc750ec855ea02f42dc90c8b3bd","tid":1377600,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"要時間俾市民係心理上做準備<br />\n<br />\n805 好啲，會多啲市民響應"},{"pid":"501718df86b2cacbfc1c681671f4e58348e76105","tid":1377600,"uid":155580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"專登打錯805迫人揀730咩意思，罷工一次失敗就破壞互信唔衰得要好好planning"},{"pid":"eb03803a5e7029a441496085d99dcf61076120a3","tid":1377600,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd45c5a2c8ab6338073c49e38d4d6532f793bc9","tid":1377600,"uid":60376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:48:09.000Z","msg":"805合理d喎 咁短時間你當文宣係神咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:05:30.000Z","msg":"我都覺得要比d時間同心理準備<br />\n因為一罷係要罷到政府跪低<br />\n你唔洗時間去買d野食買d米咩"},{"pid":"1b541e8c733a0bf210ec2da26b3f6d50398d7711","tid":1377600,"uid":90971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"其實去到呢個地步唔係應該無限期罷工咩？"},{"pid":"6721ccdff4032a9dd747eab8c9dd0927233c1c53","tid":1377600,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，唔該大家真係思考下。<br />\n仲要今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒做少少文宣係關於香港獨立，不過要soft啲係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}